Posted on June 15, 2009Wayzata Investment Partners appeals sale of Foamex to MatlinPatterson 

After being passed over in an auction to acquire Foamex earlier this month, Wayzata Investment Partners is appealing the sale of the company to MatlinPatterson, as reported in an article by Law360. 
For background information, read ‚ÄúWayzata Investment Partners lose Foamex, gain Caraustar‚Äù on Wayzata.com.    
