Posted on March 4, 2009Law360.com: Lenders Fight To Block Propex Asset Sale Plan 

Law360 is reporting:
Objections have been filed to bankrupt Propex Inc.√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢s request to approve bidding procedures that could pave the way for an affiliate of the company√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢s debtor-in-possession lender Wayzata Investment Partners LLC to buy the construction materials manufacturer for more than $61 million. 
