Company Overview of Wayzata Investment Partners LLC



Snapshot¬†People




Company Overview
Wayzata Investment Partners LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It manages private equity funds and hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity, private equity, and hedging markets of the United States. It focuses its investments in the small- and middle-market sectors and distressed markets, typically in the debt securities of distressed companies, which are in bankruptcy or undergoing financial restructuring or reorganization and undervalued debt and equity. Wayzata Investment Partners LLC was formed in 1997 and is based in Wayzata, Minnesota with additional offices in Boston, Houston in United St...
Wayzata Investment Partners LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It manages private equity funds and hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity, private equity, and hedging markets of the United States. It focuses its investments in the small- and middle-market sectors and distressed markets, typically in the debt securities of distressed companies, which are in bankruptcy or undergoing financial restructuring or reorganization and undervalued debt and equity. Wayzata Investment Partners LLC was formed in 1997 and is based in Wayzata, Minnesota with additional offices in Boston, Houston in United States, London, UK, and Mumbai, India.
